{{Quote|CorSec's Tactical Response Teams are the best.|[[Sergeant/Legends|Sergeant]] [[Volos]]|<ref name="TOR:StS">{{TORcite|type=faction|Republic|Shatter the Siege|Corellia}}</ref>}}
The '''Tactical Response Team''' ('''TRT''') was an elite commando-pilot unit of [[Corellian Security Force|CorSec]], similar to the future [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]].

==Description==
The Tactical Response Team was an elite paramilitary unit made of the most skilled members of the [[Corellian Security Force]]. It was a hybrid group that encompassed [[Commando/Legends|commandos]], [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]] and [[Detective/Legends|investigators]] trained in both police and military tactics. Contrary to the majority of CorSec officers, they operated throughout the [[Corellian system/Legends|Corellian system]] and collaborated actively with local military and police forces. TRT members were usually assigned to the most difficult CorSec missions, such as infiltrating criminal syndicates or hunting space [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]].<ref name="SoF">''[[Suns of Fortune]]''</ref>

Tactical Response Team members usually wore reinforced [[Flight suit/Legends|flight suit]]s. They were equipped with [[Blaster carbine/Legends|blaster carbines]], [[Heavy blaster pistol/Legends|heavy blaster pistols]], [[Vibroknife/Legends|vibroknives]] and [[Comlink/Legends|comlinks]].<ref name="SoF" /> 

==History==
{{Quote|CorSec had its own Tactical Response Team. Wanting to make Rogue Squadron into something similar explains why some of us made it when others didn't.|[[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]]|<ref name="XW:RS">''[[X-Wing: Rogue Squadron]]''</ref>}}
[[File:TacticalResponseTeam-TotC.jpg|thumb|right|220px|[[Major/Legends|Major]] [[Alana Walden|Walden]], a member of the Tactical Response Team in action.]]
During the [[Battle of Corellia]] that took place during the [[Galactic War]] between the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] and the [[Sith Empire (Post–Great Hyperspace War)|Sith Empire]], the Tactical Response Team fought Imperial forces alongside Republic troops in [[Coronet City/Legends|Coronet City]]'s [[Governmental Sector|Government District]].<ref name="TOR:StS" /> During the battle, a TRT squad was totally annihilated in the [[One CorSec Plaza/Legends|CorSec Headquarters]] while attempting to protect [[Commissioner/Legends|Commissioner]] [[Jonah Carter]] from an Imperial [[Hunter (individual)|bounty hunter]].<ref name="TOR:TTBL">{{TORcite|type=class|Bounty Hunter|The Thin Blue Line|Corellia}}</ref>

During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], [[Major/Legends|Major]] [[Alana Walden]] was a member of the Tactical Response Team.<ref name="AW">{{SWGTCG|set=Agents of Deception|cardname=Alana Walden|swglink=Alana Walden (Avatar) (card).JPG}}</ref><ref name="TRT">{{SWGTCG|set=Threat of the Conqueror|cardname=Tactical Response Team}}</ref> In [[5 ABY/Legends|5 ABY]], the CorSec Tactical Response Team was one of the inspiration for the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]'s reformed [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]].<ref name="XW:RS" />

